{"article_id":"xpbPqN3ZNAvUqbRv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democratic presidential frontrunner Joe Biden has a double-digit percentage lead in nearly every major national poll ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"he ' s won more big-name endorsements than his intra-party rivals in early-voting states ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and he ' s already demonstrated his prowess as a capable fundraiser .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Yet in the early going , the former vice president seems wary of his position as the favorite","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to win the 2020 Democratic presidential nomination","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and cognizant of an ailment","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that 's beleaguered once promising White House hopefuls of past years :","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Frontrunner Flameout .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" This is a marathon , \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Biden told supporters at a campaign fundraiser in Los Angeles last week .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" I know","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"all that polling stuff looks good ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"but it is a marathon","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and we have a long way to go . \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"History shows","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that the former vice president is prudent not to put too much stock into his exalted position in the very early going of the crowded 2020 presidential race .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Back in late May 2015 , Donald Trump was sitting in eighth place in the crowded Republican contest ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"according to a Quinnipiac poll .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Former Florida Gov . Jeb Bush , neurosurgeon Ben Carson , former Arkansas Gov . Mike Huckabee , U.S. Sen. Marco Rubio of Florida and Wisconsin Gov . Scott Walker were among those","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"polling ahead of him .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"At the time , 21 % of Republicans said","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"there was \" no way \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"they ' d support Trump .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"The poll showed","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that Democrat Hillary Clinton would beat him 50 % to 32 %","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"if Trump emerged as the GOP nominee .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"In June 2007 , Clinton had a 11-percentage point lead over the upstart Sen. Barack Obama ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and her fellow New Yorker Rudy Giuliani was leading the GOP field ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"according to a national Gallup poll .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Connecticut Sen. Joe Lieberman was atop the pack of Democratic hopefuls in June 2003 ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"with 20 % of Democrats supporting Lieberman for their party 's 2004 presidential nomination .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Fifteen percent supported Missouri Rep. Dick Gephardt ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"while 13 % supported the eventual nominee , Massachusetts Sen. John Kerry ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"according to Gallup .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"\" Uneasy lies the head","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that wears the crown , \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"said Christopher Borick , director of the Muhlenberg College Institute of Public Opinion .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" Everybody is targeting you .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Everybody is focusing on you .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"You take more hits","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"when you ' re in front .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Do you want to be ahead right now","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"if you ' re Joe Biden ?","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"I ' d say","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"yes ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"but you also don ' t want to be approaching it as an impregnable place","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"to sit ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"because the record says","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"it ' s not . \"","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Democratic target :","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Joe Biden is the 2020 Democratic front-runner .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Now he has a target on his back .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Credit card politics :","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Bernie Sanders , AOC unveil legislation","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"to cap credit card interest at 15 %","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Since announcing his candidacy last month ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Biden has steered clear of jousting with rival Democrats","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"and kept his aim squarely on Trump on the campaign trail .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The strategy","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"of punching at Trump , and only Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"has come","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"even as fellow Democrats continue to jab at Biden .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Sen. Elizabeth Warren has hit Biden for being \" on the side of the credit card companies \" for his backing of the 2005 Bankruptcy Abuse Prevention and Consumer Protection Act , legislation","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"that tightened rules","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"on who could qualify for bankruptcy protection .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"who is running second to Biden in most major polls ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"has tried to poke holes into Biden ' s pitch to voters","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that he ' s a champion of the middle class","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"by highlighting Biden ' s support for NAFTA and Permanent Normal Trade Relations with China during his time in the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"More recently , Biden has faced criticism from progressive groups as well as 2020 hopefuls ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"including Sanders and Washington Gov . Jay Inslee ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"after an adviser to his campaign told Reuters","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that Biden would seek a \" middle ground \" approach","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to combating climate change .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Biden has yet to detail what his climate policy will look like .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"\" The Obama-Biden Administration made historic progress on climate change , from record investment in renewable energy , to Clean Car Standards to the Paris Agreement , \"","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Inslee said .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" But the times and science have changed .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"We can not simply go back to the past ;","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"we need a bold climate plan for our future . \"","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Like what you ' re reading ?","depth":3},{"id":82,"text":"Download the app for more","depth":3},{"id":83,"text":"Biden pushed back against suggestions","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"he ' s not sufficiently committed to the issue , one","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that is particularly resonating with the younger electorate .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"He spoke specifically during a campaign stop in New Hampshire about criticism from Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"who called a `` middle ground '' approach on climate change a `` dealbreaker .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"'' `` You never heard me say 'middle of the road .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"' I ' ve never been middle of the road on the environment , ''","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Biden told reporters .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"`` Tell her to check the statements","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that I made","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and look at my record .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"She 'll find","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"that nobody has been more consistent about taking on the environment and the green revolution","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"than I have . ''","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"At the core of Biden ' s message is that he offers the Democrat ' s the best chance","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"to beat Trump","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and take back the White House .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"That message appeals to older and moderate voters","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"- who will make up a large part of the electorate in early caucuses and primary states -","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"and may be enough","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"to help Biden buck the recent trend of early frontrunners fizzling ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"said Susan MacManus , a political scientist at the University of South Florida .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Biden also benefits from the large field","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"fracturing the support of more liberal Democratic voters .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Republican awakening :","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Joe Biden :","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Republicans will have 'an epiphany '","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"after Trump leaves White House","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"But MacManus said","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"that the moderate appeal","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"that could propel Biden to his party 's nomination","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"may also prove to be his Achilles heel in the general election ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"when young voter enthusiasm will be essential for Democrats hopes","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"of taking the White House .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Voters ages 18 to 23 are projected to make up 1 in 10 eligible voters in 2020 .","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"\" We ' re going to see how deep the generation divide is in the country , \"","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"MacManus said .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"\" Younger people care less about the idea of electability","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"than sticking to principles","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"and supporting someone","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"who shares their values and goals and aspirations .","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"I doubt","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"a lot of the younger people are looking at candidates","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"and saying ,","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"' Can he ( or she )","depth":17},{"id":129,"text":"beat Trump ? ' \"","depth":17},{"id":130,"text":"Borick , the Muhlenberg College pollster , counters","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"that electability is Biden ' s greatest asset","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"and the universal desire among those on the left","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"to beat Trump","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"suggests","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"that even the most liberal voters will come around to Biden for the general election .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"we ' ve seen in previous polling a party more driven","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"by unseating the incumbent president","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"than we do now , \"","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Borick said .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"For his part , Biden has tried to stake a position above the Democratic fray ,","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"repeatedly promising to refrain from speaking ill of his 21 major Democratic Party rivals .","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"as the campaign unfolds ,","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"it will undoubtedly become more difficult to ignore incoming fire from rivals .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"Democrats are scheduled to hold their first debate of the election cycle next month in Miami ,","depth":6},{"id":147,"text":"where his Democratic rivals will seek to contrast themselves with the frontrunner .","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"Last week , Sanders and Ocasio-Cortez introduced legislation","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"to cap credit card interest rates at 15 % .","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"During the rollout of the proposed legislation , Sanders described credit card and bank industry executives as \" loan shark hoodlums '' in three-piece suits .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"The legislation will give Sanders an opportunity","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"to draw another distinction between him and Biden","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"if they end up on the same debate stage .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"( Because of the unwieldy number of candidates","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"vying for the Democratic nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"the debates are scheduled to be split over two nights","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"and Biden and Sanders aren ' t guaranteed to appear together . )","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"Trump vs. Buttigieg :","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"Mike Pence :","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"If Buttigieg wins nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"'we ' ll have a lot more to say about him '","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"Fox News :","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"The unlikely new power player in the 2020 Democratic primary","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"The youngest candidate in the race , South Bend , Indiana , Mayor Pete Buttigieg , has repeatedly made the case","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"that the country needs generational change ,","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"because the politics of the moment will decide how the next 30 or 40 years will go .","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Buttigieg , 37 , has frequently reminded voters","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"that he ' s 35 years junior to Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"and likely be alive","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"to see the impact of the big policy decisions .","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"Left unsaid by Buttigieg is that both Biden , 76 , and Sanders , 77 , are even older than Trump .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"More :","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"4 decades separate 2020 's presidential candidates .","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"Here 's what that looks like .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"Biden has said","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"he wants to assure voters","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"that he ' s not too old","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"to serve as president ,","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"and has already urged Americans to watch his vigor on the campaign trail .","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"Campaigning in Somersworth , N.H.","depth":4},{"id":182,"text":"Monday , Biden offered a folksy aside about Satchel Paige , the famous pitcher","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"who made his Major League Baseball debut at the ripe age of 42","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"after the league began integrating ,","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"to downplay the importance of age .","depth":6},{"id":186,"text":"Biden recalled a memorable exchange between Paige and reporters","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"who were marveling","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"after Paige became the oldest pitcher","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"to record a win in big league history at the age of 47","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"- a record","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"that was later broken .","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"\" 'Boys , I do n't look at age that way. \"","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"said Biden ,","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"paraphrasing the back-and-forth between Paige and the reporters .","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"\" I look at it this way ,","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"'How old would you be","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"if you did n't know","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"how old you were ? ' ``","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"Follow national political reporter Aamer Madhani on Twitter :","depth":4},{"id":200,"text":"@ AamerISmad","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":283,"right":400,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":281,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":214,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":203,"right":213,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":0,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":213,"left":207,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren